---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="RT Library Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the RT Library co-op catalog app."
  path="/apps/rt-library/privacy"
>
  <article class="container prose">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="page-header__kicker">RT Library · Legal</p>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">RT Library Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lead">
        RT Library is a co-op shareholder-built catalog app for the shared
        library room at Riviera Towers West New York, a private co-op building.
      </p>
    </header>

    <p class="updated">Effective date: July 9, 2026</p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>
      RT Library does not collect personal information in version 1.0. The app
      does not require an account, sign-in, location access, contacts, camera
      access, photo library access, microphone access, or notification
      permission.
    </p>

    <h2>Catalog Data</h2>
    <p>
      The book catalog is bundled with the app and was generated from recent
      shelf photos using OCR and metadata lookup. Searches happen on the device.
    </p>

    <h2>Network Content</h2>
    <p>
      When available, the app may load book cover images or metadata links from
      public catalog sources. RT Library does not use this to track users.
    </p>

    <h2>Requests and Availability</h2>
    <p>
      Book requests and shared availability updates are marked Coming soon and
      are not submitted or synced in version 1.0.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Email:
      <a href="mailto:srikantha.ballani@gmail.com"
        >srikantha.ballani@gmail.com</a
      >
    </p>

    <div class="links-row">
      <a href="/apps/rt-library/support">Support</a>
      <a href="/apps/rt-library">RT Library</a>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
